00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:22,190
Xichi's here to see you.

322
00:25:22,190 --> 00:25:23,150
Get up.

323
00:25:24,990 --> 00:25:26,150
Coming.

324
00:25:27,150 --> 00:25:28,190
What are you doing?

325
00:25:28,260 --> 00:25:28,950
Can't you let me

326
00:25:28,950 --> 00:25:29,820
