327
00:25:29,820 --> 00:25:31,300
It's noon, and you're still sleeping?

328
00:25:31,670 --> 00:25:32,300
I'm telling you.

329
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:33,500
Song and I have already

330
00:25:33,500 --> 00:25:34,640
