359
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:27,060
Who will like you?

360
00:26:36,150 --> 00:26:37,150
See this little boy

361
00:26:37,150 --> 00:26:38,150
in the photo?

362
00:26:38,710 --> 00:26:40,060
Let me introduce you formally.

363
00:26:40,260 --> 00:26:41,740
He's my Sishui's childhood friend.

364
00:26:41,870 --> 00:26:42,950
His name is Yu.

365
00:26:42,980 --> 00:26:44,880
I get along the best
with him in all of Sishui.

366
00:26:45,060 --> 00:26:46,910
He was so good-looking
when he was a kid.

367
00:26:47,100 --> 00:26:49,100
Fair-skinned and clean,
and he has big eyes.

368
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:50,740
And he's particularly popular.

369
00:26:50,870 --> 00:26:53,390
The people there call him
the Prince of Sishui.

370
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:57,940
Those who were good-looking
when they were young

371
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,620
usually grow up to be ugly, okay?

372
00:27:00,470 --> 00:27:02,300
Why do you sound

373
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:03,500
a bit jealous?

374
00:27:03,630 --> 00:27:04,500
I'm not jealous.

375
00:27:05,630 --> 00:27:06,300
Besides,

376
00:27:06,980 --> 00:27:08,260
no matter how close you were,

377
00:27:08,300 --> 00:27:10,120
you haven't been
in touch for years, right?

378
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:11,920
Who said we haven't been in touch?

379
00:27:11,920 --> 00:27:14,060
We just got in touch yesterday.
He's visiting today.

380
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:15,780
He's visiting you today?

381
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:17,020
Later.

382
00:27:17,190 --> 00:27:17,950
Later?

383
00:27:20,380 --> 00:27:21,740
Why didn't you tell me just now?

384
00:27:21,990 --> 00:27:22,820
You didn't ask.

385
00:27:23,470 --> 00:27:24,230
Huan'er.

386
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:26,230
Yu is downstairs.

387
00:27:26,340 --> 00:27:27,340
Help me get him.

388
00:27:28,780 --> 00:27:29,190
Wait.

389
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:30,870
Yu, right?

390
00:27:31,820 --> 00:27:32,840
Let me meet him first.

391
00:27:33,670 --> 00:27:34,470
What Yu?

392
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:43,990
Are you

393
00:27:44,150 --> 00:27:45,540
the Prince of Sishui?

394
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:48,540
I'm Jing Xichi.

395
00:27:48,870 --> 00:27:50,060
I'm Chen Huan'er's neighbor

396
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:51,740
and best friend.

397
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:53,340
I'm probably older than you.

398
00:27:53,430 --> 00:27:54,710
You can call me Big Boss Chi.

399
00:27:56,950 --> 00:27:58,580
When it comes to brotherhood among men,

400
00:27:59,060 --> 00:28:00,300
it's not about age,

401
00:28:00,630 --> 00:28:01,580
but about ability.

402
00:28:16,100 --> 00:28:16,870
Yu.

403
00:28:17,990 --> 00:28:18,580
You're here.

404
00:28:18,580 --> 00:28:20,400
Come on.
We've waited for you for a long time.

405
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:20,920
Let's go.

406
00:28:21,470 --> 00:28:21,910
This way.

407
00:28:22,910 --> 00:28:23,540
I'm telling you.

408
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:24,960
My parents kept talking about you.

409
00:28:35,230 --> 00:28:35,950
Yu.

410
00:28:35,990 --> 00:28:37,760
You must be tired
from your journey here.

411
00:28:37,950 --> 00:28:38,580
I'm alright.

412
00:28:42,580 --> 00:28:43,870
Do as I say. You hear me?

413
00:28:44,340 --> 00:28:45,100
What are you up to?

414
00:28:49,710 --> 00:28:50,670
How cute.

415
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:51,630
Fair and chubby.

416
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:52,780
You're more handsome.

417
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:53,630
Be gentle.

418
00:28:54,260 --> 00:28:56,320
You're even more handsome
as you grow up.

419
00:28:56,860 --> 00:28:57,710
How did it go?

420
00:28:57,900 --> 00:28:58,910
How did you do in Gaokao?

421
00:28:59,120 --> 00:28:59,870
I did alright.

422
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:00,990
I performed as usual.

423
00:29:01,500 --> 00:29:02,740
You'll be okay then. Here.

424
00:29:03,020 --> 00:29:03,780
Have a strawberry.

425
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:05,230
No.

426
00:29:06,100 --> 00:29:06,870
Eat it.

427
00:29:08,470 --> 00:29:09,260
Chen Huan'er.

428
00:29:09,470 --> 00:29:10,060
How obedient.

429
00:29:10,300 --> 00:29:12,670
Can you be a little more reserved?

430
00:29:13,260 --> 00:29:13,870
What's wrong?

431
00:29:13,980 --> 00:29:15,080
We slept in the same bed

432
00:29:15,080 --> 00:29:15,950
