433
00:29:15,990 --> 00:29:17,740
Right? Yu.

434
00:29:18,500 --> 00:29:19,500
Right?

435
00:29:19,740 --> 00:29:20,780
Yes, you're right.

436
00:29:22,910 --> 00:29:24,020
Chen Huan'er.

437
00:29:24,470 --> 00:29:26,430
You're really a weirdo.

438
00:29:27,150 --> 00:29:27,470
Here.

439
00:29:27,710 --> 00:29:28,150
Yu.

440
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,060
Have another one.

441
00:29:29,910 --> 00:29:30,910
