444
00:29:34,670 --> 00:29:35,340
How obedient.

445
00:29:36,740 --> 00:29:38,340
Chen Huan'er, did you do it on purpose?

446
00:29:38,460 --> 00:29:39,500
What am I doing on purpose?

447
00:29:39,500 --> 00:29:40,710
Why are you

448
00:29:40,780 --> 00:29:41,740
