450
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:44,320
If you don't like it, don't watch.

451
00:29:44,630 --> 00:29:45,470
Food's ready.

452
00:29:46,190 --> 00:29:46,820
Xichi.

453
00:29:47,240 --> 00:29:48,340
Uncle Chen isn't around.

454
00:29:48,390 --> 00:29:50,140
We're only having a simple meal at home.

455
00:29:50,140 --> 00:29:50,840
Sure, Aunt Lina.

456
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:51,540
Where's Yu?

457
00:29:52,230 --> 00:29:52,950
Toilet.

458
00:29:53,340 --> 00:29:54,190
Yu.

459
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:55,390
Food's ready.

460
00:29:56,540 --> 00:29:58,100
Hurry. Here, eat.

461
00:29:58,540 --> 00:29:59,150
Yu.

462
00:29:59,300 --> 00:29:59,870
Here.

463
00:30:00,230 --> 00:30:00,670
Sit here.

464
00:30:01,670 --> 00:30:02,740
