- Here, Yu.

465
00:30:03,020 --> 00:30:03,740
Sit with me.

466
00:30:03,990 --> 00:30:05,060
Here, sit beside me.

467
00:30:06,740 --> 00:30:08,870
Mom's cooking smells so good.

468
00:30:09,910 --> 00:30:11,670
You must eat more, Yu.

469
00:30:16,740 --> 00:30:17,390
Yu.

470
00:30:17,780 --> 00:30:19,780
It's your first time here
since we moved here.

471
00:30:20,500 --> 00:30:21,390
It's nice here, right?

472
00:30:21,500 --> 00:30:22,580
I looked around just now.

473
00:30:22,580 --> 00:30:23,820
The environment here is good.

474
00:30:23,840 --> 00:30:24,560
Right?

475
00:30:25,220 --> 00:30:26,540
You've lost weight. Eat more.

476
00:30:26,580 --> 00:30:27,060
Sure.

477
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:28,870
Aunt Lina.

478
00:30:28,870 --> 00:30:30,430
You don't have to help me with the food.

479
00:30:30,450 --> 00:30:32,420
I'm familiar with this place.
I come here often.

480
00:30:32,420 --> 00:30:33,300
I can do it myself.

481
00:30:34,990 --> 00:30:36,540
Here, Yu. Eat more.

482
00:30:36,780 --> 00:30:38,060
Isn't this your favorite meat?

483
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:38,710
Eat more.

484
00:30:40,150 --> 00:30:40,910
Yu.

485
00:30:41,540 --> 00:30:43,300
Stay a few more days since you're here.

486
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,300
Spend more time with Huan'er.

487
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:46,540
Sure.

488
00:30:48,470 --> 00:30:49,230
Aunt Lina.

489
00:30:50,190 --> 00:30:51,300
Let Yu

490
00:30:51,670 --> 00:30:52,820
