491
00:30:56,630 --> 00:30:58,020
Why should Yu stay at your place?

492
00:30:59,950 --> 00:31:00,820
I just think

493
00:31:01,470 --> 00:31:02,630
Yu's a guy.

494
00:31:02,780 --> 00:31:03,580
Surely it would be

495
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,660
