at his aunt's and cousin's house?

502
00:31:15,780 --> 00:31:16,620
You're funny.

503
00:31:18,910 --> 00:31:20,500
What did you call Aunt Lina?

504
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:21,060
Auntie Lina.

505
00:31:22,820 --> 00:31:25,150
So Chen Huan'er is your...

506
00:31:25,230 --> 00:31:26,260
Cousin.

507
00:31:26,260 --> 00:31:26,870
Yeah.

508
00:31:31,800 --> 00:31:32,580
Nothing, Aunt Lina.

509
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:33,190
I... Well...

510
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:34,140
The food looks good.

511
00:31:34,140 --> 00:31:34,800
No, well...

512
00:31:34,910 --> 00:31:35,630
The sun is nice.

513
00:31:35,670 --> 00:31:36,470
No, I got to go.

514
00:31:36,500 --> 00:31:37,390
I got to go, Aunt Lina.

515
00:31:38,260 --> 00:31:38,670
Well...

516
00:31:41,020 --> 00:31:42,100
What's come over him?

517
00:31:43,260 --> 00:31:44,150
Nothing.

518
00:31:45,990 --> 00:31:46,710
Here.

519
00:31:47,020 --> 00:31:47,580
You did good.

520
00:31:47,870 --> 00:31:48,430
Have a prawn.

521
00:31:49,020 --> 00:31:49,430
Here.

522
00:31:50,470 --> 00:31:52,060
Why are you so strange today?

523
00:31:52,620 --> 00:31:53,670
