524
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:57,950
You're overly enthusiastic.

525
00:31:58,220 --> 00:31:59,580
Did you take the wrong pill?

526
00:31:59,670 --> 00:32:00,390
Hey!

527
00:32:01,020 --> 00:32:01,910
Don't ask so much. Eat.

528
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:02,710
