533
00:32:19,470 --> 00:32:19,990
Sit.

534
00:32:27,020 --> 00:32:28,100
Why are you looking at me?

535
00:32:29,060 --> 00:32:30,950
Has Prince of Sishui left?

536
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:32,150
Yeah.

537
00:32:32,420 --> 00:32:34,000
He left after staying for two days.

538
00:32:35,540 --> 00:32:36,670
Prince of Sishui?

539
00:32:39,360 --> 00:32:41,020
She said he was her childhood friend

540
00:32:41,150 --> 00:32:42,580
and her best friend,

541
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:43,980
but he's actually her cousin.

542
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:45,190
Chen Huan'er.

543
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,430
Don't you think you're silly?

544
00:32:46,500 --> 00:32:47,900
Do you think it's funny to trick me?

545
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:49,150
Didn't you say it first?

546
00:32:49,150 --> 00:32:50,480
You said I don't behave like a girl

547
00:32:50,480 --> 00:32:51,620
and that nobody will like me.

548
00:32:51,620 --> 00:32:52,040
Song.

549
00:32:52,260 --> 00:32:53,950
In what way do I not behave like a girl?

550
00:32:53,950 --> 00:32:54,670
How am I

551
00:32:54,670 --> 00:32:55,710
not worthy of being liked?

552
00:32:56,150 --> 00:32:56,990
You're...

553
00:32:57,540 --> 00:32:58,190
worthy.

554
00:32:58,870 --> 00:32:59,630
Ignore him.

555
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:01,150
He's just blind.

556
00:33:02,300 --> 00:33:03,910
Look, Song said it himself.

557
00:33:04,060 --> 00:33:04,710
Song Cong.

558
00:33:05,430 --> 00:33:06,820
I'm upset that you said that.

559
00:33:07,340 --> 00:33:09,300
I was even planning
to help you get rich.

560
00:33:09,910 --> 00:33:10,580
Get rich?

561
00:33:11,500 --> 00:33:12,190
How?

562
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:14,820
Didn't I tell you a few days ago

563
00:33:14,910 --> 00:33:16,540
that I was going to sell
all our school's

564
00:33:16,540 --> 00:33:17,980
supplementary teaching materials?

565
00:33:17,980 --> 00:33:18,910
But then I thought,

566
00:33:19,190 --> 00:33:20,230
no.

567
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,420
Think about it.

568
00:33:21,500 --> 00:33:22,500
Song's notes

569
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:23,990
are priceless.

570
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:25,230
If we sell it by weight,

571
00:33:25,230 --> 00:33:26,380
